Partner Collaboration

Celebrating the Official Opening of the National Gallery

Published on Jan 28, 2016

Celebrating the Official Opening of the National Gallery

In conjunction with the official opening celebrations of the National Gallery in November 2015, SOTA Music students put up a percussion performance at the National Gallery. Five of our Visual Arts students also interned at the National Gallery during this period and gained valuable experience working at the newest major arts institution in Singapore.
